title: S12 Ep148: The 40 Year Resurrection of Elvis
itunes:title: The 40 Year Resurrection of Elvis
description:
Wayback Week jumps into conspiracy theory territory! This week marks the 40th anniversary of Elvis Presley's death... or does it? Author/Researcher Gail Brewer-Giorgio, the quintessential Elvis conspiracy theorist, joins the program to break down the case and make the argument for why he is still alive, and could possibly come back...
